    <abstract id="aspace_3ac03730e34fb683348807facb9028da">Videotapes of films made by the Division of Community Education, many of them directed by Jack Delano. Some are documentaries on current developments in Puerto Rican performing and visual arts; others are evidently fictional.</abstract>
